5.24.25  1:42 am   what is your wisdom of the day, oh great wurtz man

      never make the 'quality' of your art too good. the viewer enjoys using their imagination to fill in the rest of the quality. they'll even convince themself that you'd imagined it the same way, and they'll thank you for imagining it that way, and putting it into their head
